SUMMARY:Winters Chapter Shut Up and Write
DESCRIPTION:Winters Shut Up and Write Meetup Group\nCome to the Winters Co
 mmunity Library on March 18\, 2026 at 5 pm and help us launch the Winters 
 chapter of Shut Up and Write. This is an inclusive group - all genres\, al
 l levels of experience.\n\nAgenda:\n1.Arrive\, settle in\nBrief introducti
 ons: name and\, if you like\, what you're working on\nSet a small\, achiev
 able writing goal for yourself for the session\n2 Writing. No talking\, no
  critiques. Just writing.\n3\\. Wrap up and Celebration\nBrief check-in. S
 hare what was accomplished or how the session went - it's about personal p
 rogress\, not perfection!
